#: InputStream category
msgctxt "#30660"
msgid "InputStream"
msgstr "InputStream"

msgctxt "#30661"
msgid "InputStream addon"
msgstr "InputStream-tilføjelse"

msgctxt "#30662"
msgid "The InputStream addon to use for playback. FFmpeg Direct supports timeshift with a local device buffer. Adaptive supports timeshift with a server-side buffer. FFmpeg (Kodi internal) does not support timeshift."
msgstr "Den InputStream-tilføjelse, der skal bruges til afspilning. FFmpeg Direct understøtter tidsforskydning med en lokal buffer på enheden. Adaptive understøtter tidsforskydning med en buffer på serversiden. FFmpeg (intern i Kodi) understøtter ikke tidsforskydning."

msgctxt "#30663"
msgid "FFmpeg Direct"
msgstr "FFmpeg Direct"

msgctxt "#30664"
msgid "Adaptive"
msgstr "Adaptive"

msgctxt "#30665"
msgid "FFmpeg (Kodi internal)"
msgstr "FFmpeg (intern i Kodi)"

msgctxt "#30666"
msgid "Enable timeshift"
msgstr "Aktivér tidsforskydning"

msgctxt "#30667"
msgid "Buffer the live stream from the point playback began. Buffer is created on the client, control the maximum size through inputstream.ffmpegdirect settings."
msgstr "Buffrer live-streamen fra det punkt, hvor afspilningen begyndte. Bufferen oprettes på klienten; styr den maksimale størrelse via indstillingerne for inputstream.ffmpegdirect."

msgctxt "#30668"
msgid "In-progress recording InputStream"
msgstr "InputStream til igangværende optagelse"

msgctxt "#30669"
msgid "The InputStream to use for in-progress recording playback. Adaptive can skip forward through an in-progress recording. FFmpeg cannot skip ahead but may be more robust."
msgstr "Den InputStream, der skal bruges til afspilning af igangværende optagelser. Adaptive kan spole frem i en igangværende optagelse. FFmpeg kan ikke spole frem, men er muligvis mere robust."

#: Advanced category
msgctxt "#30670"
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Avanceret"

msgctxt "#30672"
msgid "Channel reload interval (hours)"
msgstr "Interval for genindlæsning af kanaler (timer)"

msgctxt "#30673"
msgid "How often to reload channel data from Jellyfin."
msgstr "Hvor ofte kanaldata genindlæses fra Jellyfin."

msgctxt "#30674"
msgid "Connection check timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Timeout for forbindelsestjek (sekunder)"

msgctxt "#30675"
msgid "How long to wait for a response when checking the Jellyfin server connection."
msgstr "Hvor længe der ventes på et svar ved tjek af forbindelsen til Jellyfin-serveren."

msgctxt "#30676"
msgid "Connection check interval (seconds)"
msgstr "Interval for forbindelsestjek (sekunder)"

msgctxt "#30677"
msgid "How often to check if the Jellyfin server is reachable."
msgstr "Hvor ofte der tjekkes, om Jellyfin-serveren kan nås."

#: Account category
msgctxt "#30700"
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Konto"

msgctxt "#30701"
msgid "Server address"
msgstr "Serveradresse"

msgctxt "#30702"
msgid "The URL of your Jellyfin server."
msgstr "URL'en til din Jellyfin-server."

msgctxt "#30703"
msgid "Login"
msgstr "Log ind"

msgctxt "#30704"
msgid "Server name"
msgstr "Servernavn"

msgctxt "#30705"
msgid "Logout"
msgstr "Log ud"

msgctxt "#30706"
msgid "Username/Password"
msgstr "Brugernavn/adgangskode"

msgctxt "#30707"
msgid "Quick Connect"
msgstr "Quick Connect"

msgctxt "#30708"
msgid "Choose login method"
msgstr "Vælg loginmetode"

msgctxt "#30709"
msgid "Enter username"
msgstr "Indtast brugernavn"

msgctxt "#30710"
msgid "Enter password"
msgstr "Indtast adgangskode"

msgctxt "#30711"
msgid "Login successful! Restart addon to connect."
msgstr "Login lykkedes! Genstart tilføjelsen for at oprette forbindelse."

msgctxt "#30712"
msgid "Logged out successfully."
msgstr "Du er nu logget ud."

msgctxt "#30713"
msgid "Login failed. Check credentials."
msgstr "Login mislykkedes. Tjek loginoplysningerne."

msgctxt "#30714"
msgid "Enter a server address first."
msgstr "Indtast først en serveradresse."

msgctxt "#30715"
msgid "Opus"
msgstr "Opus"

msgctxt "#30716"
msgid "Username"
msgstr "Brugernavn"

msgctxt "#30717"
msgid "Test Connection"
msgstr "Test forbindelse"

msgctxt "#30720"
msgid "Transcode H264 10-bit (Hi10P)"
msgstr "Transkod H264 10-bit (Hi10P)"

msgctxt "#30721"
msgid "Force transcoding of H264 10-bit content. Enable if your device doesn't support Hi10P decoding."
msgstr "Tvinger transkodning af H264-10-bit-indhold. Aktivér, hvis din enhed ikke understøtter Hi10P-afkodning."

msgctxt "#30722"
msgid "Transcode HEVC range extensions"
msgstr "Transkod HEVC range extensions"

msgctxt "#30723"
msgid "Force transcoding of HEVC content with range extension profiles (4:2:2, 4:4:4). Enable if your device only supports Main and Main 10."
msgstr "Tvinger transkodning af HEVC-indhold med range extension-profiler (4:2:2, 4:4:4). Aktivér, hvis din enhed kun understøtter Main og Main 10."

msgctxt "#30724"
msgid "Kofin PVR Settings"
msgstr "Kofin PVR-indstillinger"

msgctxt "#30725"
msgid "FFmpeg Direct settings..."
msgstr "FFmpeg Direct-indstillinger..."

msgctxt "#30726"
msgid "Restart addon"
msgstr "Genstart tilføjelsen"

#: Catchup category
msgctxt "#30730"
msgid "Catchup"
msgstr "Catchup"

msgctxt "#30731"
msgid "Enable catchup (IPTV)"
msgstr "Aktivér catchup (IPTV)"

msgctxt "#30732"
msgid "Enable catchup/archive TV if supported by your provider. Only works with direct play, so force remuxing must be turned off and bitrate set unlimited. Requires a reference M3U file (configured in the Advanced section) that matches your Jellyfin channel names and contains catchup tags which are omitted by Jellyfin."
msgstr "Aktiverer catchup-/arkiv-tv, hvis din udbyder understøtter det. Virker kun med direkte afspilning, så tvungen remuxning skal være deaktiveret, og bithastigheden skal være indstillet til ubegrænset. Kræver en reference-M3U-fil (konfigureret i afsnittet Avanceret), der matcher dine Jellyfin-kanalnavne og indeholder catchup-tags, som udelades af Jellyfin."

msgctxt "#30733"
msgid "Reference M3U location"
msgstr "Placering af reference-M3U"

msgctxt "#30734"
msgid "Choose whether the reference M3U file is stored locally or accessed via a URL."
msgstr "Vælg, om reference-M3U-filen gemmes lokalt eller tilgås via en URL."

msgctxt "#30735"
msgid "Reference M3U file"
msgstr "Reference-M3U-fil"

msgctxt "#30736"
msgid "Path to the reference M3U file on the local filesystem."
msgstr "Sti til reference-M3U-filen i det lokale filsystem."

msgctxt "#30737"
msgid "Reference M3U URL"
msgstr "Reference-M3U-URL"

msgctxt "#30738"
msgid "URL of the reference M3U file."
msgstr "URL til reference-M3U-filen."

msgctxt "#30739"
msgid "Query format string"
msgstr "Formatstreng til forespørgsel"

msgctxt "#30740"
msgid "A provider-dependent format string for catchup URLs. Used as a default when channels don't specify their own catchup-source. E.g. &cutv={Y}-{m}-{d}T{H}:{M}:{S}"
msgstr "En udbyderafhængig formatstreng til catchup-URL'er. Bruges som standard, når kanaler ikke angiver deres egen catchup-source. F.eks. &cutv={Y}-{m}-{d}T{H}:{M}:{S}"

msgctxt "#30741"
msgid "Catchup window (days)"
msgstr "Catchup-vindue (dage)"

msgctxt "#30742"
msgid "The number of days into the past in which it is possible to catch up on a programme."
msgstr "Antallet af dage tilbage i tiden, hvor det er muligt at se et program bagudrettet."

msgctxt "#30743"
msgid "Default catchup mode for all channels"
msgstr "Standardtilstand for catchup for alle kanaler"

msgctxt "#30744"
msgid "If set, all channels are assumed to support catchup using this mode. Channels with explicit catchup tags in the M3U will use their own mode."
msgstr "Hvis dette er angivet, antages alle kanaler at understøtte catchup med denne tilstand. Kanaler med eksplicitte catchup-tags i M3U'en bruger deres egen tilstand."

msgctxt "#30745"
msgid "Play from EPG in live TV mode (timeshift)"
msgstr "Afspil fra EPG i live-tv-tilstand (tidsforskydning)"

msgctxt "#30746"
msgid "When enabled, selecting a past programme plays it as a timeshifted live stream (can skip forward/back through the catchup window). When disabled, it plays as a bounded video."
msgstr "Når dette er aktiveret, afspilles et valgt tidligere program som en tidsforskudt live-stream (det er muligt at spole frem/tilbage inden for catchup-vinduet). Når det er deaktiveret, afspilles det som en afgrænset video."

msgctxt "#30747"
msgid "Buffer before programme start (minutes)"
msgstr "Buffer før programmets start (minutter)"

msgctxt "#30748"
msgid "Extra buffer time before the programme start when playing as a bounded video."
msgstr "Ekstra buffertid før programmets start ved afspilning som afgrænset video."

msgctxt "#30749"
msgid "Buffer after programme end (minutes)"
msgstr "Buffer efter programmets slutning (minutter)"

msgctxt "#30750"
msgid "Extra buffer time after the programme end when playing as a bounded video."
msgstr "Ekstra buffertid efter programmets slutning ved afspilning som afgrænset video."

msgctxt "#30751"
msgid "Catchup only on finished programmes"
msgstr "Catchup kun for afsluttede programmer"

msgctxt "#30752"
msgid "Only allow catchup playback on programmes that have already ended. The currently airing programme cannot be watched as catchup until it finishes."
msgstr "Tillad kun catchup-afspilning for programmer, der allerede er afsluttet. Programmet, der sendes nu, kan ikke ses som catchup, før det er afsluttet."

